race.description: Yulong Jockey Club Trophy Maiden Plate
race.comment: Tricky. NINJASK (7) won two trials and then was well supported at Beaudesert on debut but spoiled things with a slow start. The local will be better for that and maps well. Should go close. USUAL LIMITS (4) led on debut in the same contest and tired late. She can run them along again and with the extra fitness will be much tougher to pass. PHIL UP (8) resumes for the Kendrick yard and expect him to come back improved. Wasn't asked for much in a recent trial and will carry just 53kg with the claim. MINTO'S PRINCE (2) debuts and has looked good at the trials. Has the inside barrier and the late betting will be key. SCOTTVILLE SCOOTER (3) resumes for a new barn and the mare ran her best race when narrowly beaten this trip on the Sunshine Coast poly. Found a place in a recent Beaudesert trial and goes into the exotics at a price.
